<h2>Three ways to engage.</h2>
<p class="lead-text" style="margin-bottom:0">The process can be applied in different ways depending on your organisation's needs, capacity, and readiness for internal ownership.</p>
<div class="models-layout">
<div class="models-photo">
<img src="/assets/img/photos/three-ways-handshake.jpg" alt="Two colleagues shaking hands across a boardroom table">
