<div class="models-col">
<div class="model-card">
<div class="model-sub">Option 1</div>
<h3>Licence only</h3>
<p>For organisations that want to apply the methodology internally. Includes access to the Engage framework and tool, with training to support self-administration from the start.</p>
</div>
<div class="model-card">
<div class="model-sub">Option 2</div>
<h3>Implementation support</h3>
<p>APAG facilitates the full process — from executive alignment through to grade conversion and handover. Best suited for first-time implementations or large, complex exercises.</p>
</div>
<div class="model-card">
<div class="model-sub">Option 3</div>
<h3>Hybrid model</h3>
<p>Implementation is supported initially, then progressively transitioned to the internal team. Combines expert guidance with a deliberate path to internal ownership.</p>
</div>
</div>
